==National team==
With the [[Yugoslav national basketball team]], Danilovi<U+0107> won four [[EuroBasket|European Championships]] in [[EuroBasket 1989|1989]], [[EuroBasket 1991|1991]], [[EuroBasket 1995|1995]] and [[EuroBasket 1997|1997]]. He was also a member of the silver medal winning Yugoslav team at the [[Basketball at the 1996 Summer Olympics|1996 Summer Olympics]] in [[Atlanta]].

